explanation: The clause only states that the Disclosing Party is not obligated to provide or update Confidential Information. It does not address whether either party is obligated to enter into any further agreement or transaction, which is the specific requirement of the rule. Therefore, the NDA fails to include the required disclaimer.
rule: Clarify that the NDA does not obligate either party to enter into any further agreement or transaction.
exampleLanguage: This Agreement does not obligate either party to enter into any further agreement or transaction.
